Dialogue: 5,0:02:25.59,0:02:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He's generally in good health.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:27.62,0:02:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be mindful of keeping him well hydrated.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:30.46,0:02:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him approximately \N400 cc of water every hour.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:34.40,0:02:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We will. Thank you for all your help.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:37.08,0:02:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The neurosurgeon comes back from the city tomorrow.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:40.90,0:02:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You should consult him as well.{the doctor is bailing here, hes telling them to go to the neurosurgeon now to be on the safe side}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:42.35,0:02:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, would it be okay for me to come along?{hes asking the doctor whether its medically acceptable to ask hikari questions and to presumably ask the surgeon questions about hikari. akari then interrupts him.}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:45.42,0:02:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I have some questions I'd like to ask Hikari{-kun}.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:47.56,0:02:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:49.27,0:02:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Hikari must be very tired since he only just woke up.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:53.89,0:02:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think we could hold off on all these tests for now?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:57.24,0:02:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 5,0:02:58.22,0:03:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just... I think he could use \Nsome time to catch up,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:02.47,0:03:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,at least a little bit.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:05.45,0:03:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:08.35,0:03:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for being so insensitive.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:11.95,0:03:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel free to call me if there are any changes.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:24.65,0:03:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that, Akira!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:28.25,0:03:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't disturb him.\N He needs his rest.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:40.47,0:03:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're acting like I'm some kinda monster.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:42.78,0:03:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I-I didn't mean—
Dialogue: 5,0:03:44.90,0:03:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm{\i0} the one who should be surprised.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:46.90,0:03:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, what the hell?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:48.36,0:03:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fourteen now?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.93,0:03:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes you the same age as me.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:51.36,0:03:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh.}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:52.37,0:03:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And Akari's got a kid now, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:54.88,0:03:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I figured stuff like this could happen during the hibernation.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:00.25,0:04:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? \NSomething wrong with your eyes?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:02.04,0:04:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mom.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:03.26,0:04:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:04.30,0:04:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:10.41,0:04:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's just so bright \Nthat it's kinda hard to see.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:13.99,0:04:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you were asleep for a while.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:17.12,0:04:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably just not used to \Nhow bright it is up here.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:20.32,0:04:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All right now, back to bed you go.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:22.16,0:04:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisaki's probably gonna stop by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:25.57,0:04:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu got so much taller.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:28.63,0:04:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisaki probably looks older now too.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:32.41,0:04:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, she's got quite the nice body now.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:34.10,0:04:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you're excited to see her!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:35.75,0:04:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why the heck would {\i1}that{\i0} matter?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:38.54,0:04:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to be shy with me.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.22,0:04:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit acting stupid.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:41.38,0:04:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're turning red!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:42.43,0:04:43.72,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's back.{overlap}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:42.86,0:04:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:44.69,0:04:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hikari's back!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:05.61,0:05:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:09.69,0:05:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't Chisaki{-san} wanna go see Hikari{-kun}?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:14.03,0:05:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she has an exam today.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:16.43,0:05:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But aren't they childhood friends?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:19.33,0:05:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That seems kinda cold.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:21.67,0:05:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought Chisaki{-san} would be dying to see him.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:34.07,0:05:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He hasn't changed at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:50.55,0:05:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:53.79,0:05:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}I'm gonna get you!{Kancho! Kancho! Kancho! Kancho!}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:56.91,0:05:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with all the noise, you two?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:00.41,0:06:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd show him how a pro does it.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.05,0:06:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Up your butt!{Kancho!}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.76,0:06:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I called Tsumugu. He said Chisaki's busy today.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:10.12,0:06:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:13.81,0:06:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.69,0:06:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If Chisaki{-san} and Tsumugu{-kun} had come by today,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:18.08,0:06:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've taken some time off so we could have a barbecue.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.28,0:06:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to do anything extravagant.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:22.18,0:06:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, we haven't even put a dent into the loan for this house.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.03,0:06:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So have a good day at work, Dad.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:30.13,0:06:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who the heck that could be.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:32.33,0:06:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:35.20,0:06:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayama?!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:37.32,0:06:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is Hikari. And he hasn't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.44,0:06:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who are you?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Sayu.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:44.24,0:06:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. Haven't I matured quite a bit?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:47.58,0:06:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it kinda gives me the creeps.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.88,0:06:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's looking forward to seeing you.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:52.76,0:06:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Teach{Sensei}, Seiki, and Akiyoshi too.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:56.20,0:06:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drive you, so why don't we go see all of 'em?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:59.14,0:07:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But Hikari hasn't fully recovered.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:02.02,0:07:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I'll go see 'em.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.44,0:07:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:04.75,0:07:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You two want a ride to school?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:07.84,0:07:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I{'ve} gotta make a few stops first, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:12.11,0:07:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:17.47,0:07:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, talk about a turn of events.{pv}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.79,0:07:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it all feels like a dream to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:23.17,0:07:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"Feels like a dream"?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.80,0:07:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you some character \Nout of a chick flick now?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.44,0:07:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean it like that!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:28.14,0:07:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Not {\i1}that{\i0} sort of a dream.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:29.92,0:07:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that this is all \Nkind of strange and unusual.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just really surprising, is all.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.91,0:07:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And right around then, \NEgawa was really getting around.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.46,0:07:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and then in high school,\N he went out with Yaragi.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:46.68,0:07:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:47.38,0:07:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He shouldn't have dated someone who lived so close, you know?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:50.20,0:07:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Honjin is working \Nat the government office now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:07.84,Oshit Oshit; Fishy Business,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\frx0\fry342\c&HD5561B&\1a&H64&\pos(720,293)\org(712,468)\fscx57\fscy57}Oshiooshi Fishery Cooperative
Dialogue: 5,0:08:05.31,0:08:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at those eyes.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.24,0:08:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Hikari, all right. He's finally back!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:11.40,0:08:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:12.72,0:08:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Hikari came back,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:15.12,0:08:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone else from the sea should come back soon too, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:18.08,0:08:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn right.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:19.38,0:08:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll finally be able to drink some nice sake with them again.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:23.00,0:08:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:24.47,0:08:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's cut out all the depressing talk so early in the morning.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:28.00,0:08:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:29.66,0:08:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,we kept this for ya.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:32.02,0:08:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Open 'er up.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:37.41,0:08:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the flag you waved at the Boatdrift Ceremony.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:40.76,0:08:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We found it stuck on the \Nbridge pier about three years ago.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.93,0:08:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii{-kun}, wave the flag.{pv}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:48.55,0:08:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wave it as much as you can.{pv}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:50.28,0:08:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, no one will get lost.{pv}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:56.83,0:08:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:59.48,0:09:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:00.70,0:09:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I just feel kinda sick.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:02.68,0:09:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:05.08,0:09:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You just woke up.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:07.46,0:09:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry, Hikari.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:09.02,0:09:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We got a little carried away.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:10.40,0:09:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:12.62,0:09:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably just need some rest.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:14.97,0:09:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Help him out, Sayama.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:16.58,0:09:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:20.28,Oshit Oshit; Fishy Business,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\frx0\fry342\c&HD5561B&\1a&H64&\pos(720,293)\org(712,468)\fscx57\fscy57}Oshiooshi Fishery Cooperative
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.61,0:09:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure this is close enough?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:20.28,0:09:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:26.04,Maschinenzimmer.412,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur1\c&H6846CC&\fscx67\fscy67\frz51.603\fsp-15.95\frx2\fry6\org(939.333,662.667)\pos(966,565)}A{\frz44.738\fsp-17.25}l{\frz37.310\fsp-22.01}w{\frz27.832\fsp-18.23}a{\frz19.984\fsp-17.96}y{\frz12.250\fsp-13.77}s{\frz6.323\fsp-15.78} {\frz-0.469\fsp-25.61}S{\frz-11.496\fsp-19.06}m{\frz-19.702\fsp-9.08}i{\frz-23.610\fsp-9.08}l{\frz-27.518\fsp-14.42}i{\frz-33.726\fsp-20.03}n{\frz-42.346\fsp0}g
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:26.04,Maschinenzimmer.412,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.18\blur1\c&H6242C2&\fscx67\fscy67\pos(939.333,668.667)\frz350.5}Saya         Mart
Dialogue: 5,0:09:21.38,0:09:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, please get Hikari home quickly.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:24.12,0:09:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sorry about this.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:25.30,0:09:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, study hard!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:33.04,0:09:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. We're already late.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:36.03,0:09:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hikari hasn't changed one bit.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:39.59,0:09:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And now I'm the same age he is.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:43.87,0:09:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But somehow...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:53.00,0:09:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari{-kun} resurfaced at this location right here, so...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:56.80,0:10:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's likely that the underwater current changes here, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:00.48,0:10:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's different from our findings last month.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:02.68,0:10:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But according to the reflection of the Tomoebi—
Dialogue: 5,0:10:06.22,0:10:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Tsumugu, do you have scissors?{61!}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:08.82,0:10:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there's a pair in Chisaki's room.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:21.51,0:10:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{Eek!}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:25.51,0:10:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:27.09,0:10:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you were back.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:29.95,0:10:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:32.53,0:10:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:35.91,0:10:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:39.05,0:10:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I look?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:42.81,0:10:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a pretty bold question.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:46.07,0:10:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I changed?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.79,0:10:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't see you like that back then, \Nso I can't really say.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:59.79,0:11:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You talked about this a lot back then, though.{ Remember?}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:03.05,0:11:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,380)}You would talk about changing, and not changing, all the time.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:08.84,0:11:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want anyone to change.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:12.68,0:11:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It was really just Hikari who I wanted to remain the same.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:18.13,0:11:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:20.64,0:11:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm{\i0} the one who's changed.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:30.61,0:11:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true. You {\i1}have{\i0} changed.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:35.93,0:11:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotten prettier.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:39.31,0:11:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You've become much more beautiful{ since back then}.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.39,0:11:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that change bad too?{"is that a problem too?". the point here is that she implies neutral or negative change while tsumugu says whatever change occurred was positive. now, how much does he like her? i think they grew close over the years, being the only ones, but its not certain whether its more than platonic affection}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:54.39,0:11:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't it be a good thing instead?{these lines show affection and a desire to console her, but they dont imply love}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:14.05,0:12:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha up to?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:16.15,0:12:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just figured I'd take a walk or something.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:18.93,0:12:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't overdo it!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:20.92,0:12:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, have you heard from Chisaki{-san}?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:23.40,0:12:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, nope, I haven't.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.77,0:12:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't quite believe it.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:27.66,0:12:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already been two whole days since Hikari came back.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:31.21,0:12:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet Hikari seems down because Chisaki{-san} hasn't come to see him.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:35.88,0:12:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And Tsumugu hasn't stopped by either.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:38.06,0:12:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can't you call them again, Mom?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:40.19,0:12:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, I can sort of understand how they feel.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:44.23,0:12:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:46.69,0:12:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Let's hurry and finish hanging these to dry.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:56.57,0:12:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Done! I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:01.13,0:13:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:12.55,0:13:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Chisaki{-san}?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:14.57,0:13:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She went to go see Gramps.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:18.84,0:13:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem troubled.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:20.22,0:13:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:21.69,0:13:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:23.14,0:13:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari came back!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:25.36,0:13:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why hasn't Chisaki{-san} gone to see him yet?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:29.23,0:13:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's something \Nyou can understand...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:32.09,0:13:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{Wh-Why not?}B-But I'm the same age as Hikari now!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:36.10,0:13:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...because I don't get it either.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:37.48,0:13:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:39.05,0:13:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two have known each \Nother for a long time.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:42.01,0:13:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There are probably things only they understand about each other.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:45.73,0:13:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm being left out again.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:47.55,0:13:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:48.26,0:13:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:31.97,0:14:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:35.19,0:14:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:37.07,0:14:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.28,0:14:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean? I was swimming.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:41.07,0:14:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why haven't you come to see Chisaki?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:43.53,0:14:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should {\i1}I{\i0} be the one to go see {\i1}her{\i0}?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:48.17,0:14:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You really haven't changed at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:50.85,0:14:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I haven't!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:55.55,0:14:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just the other day for me!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:57.77,0:15:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, the Boatdrift Ceremony was the day before yesterday! Time hasn't passed at all in my mind!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:03.34,0:15:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm overwhelmed with all this!{"I am nonplussed, and yes that is the correct meaning of the word!"}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.42,0:15:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari has a kid, and all of you have changed!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:08.67,0:15:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still summer for me, but even the \Nscenery's changed. {\i1}Everything's{\i0} changed!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:12.54,0:15:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So of course I can't just \Nwaltz in to go see Chisaki.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.17,0:15:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of us were always together!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:18.82,0:15:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If that Chisaki has changed—
Dialogue: 5,0:15:21.31,0:15:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't take seeing any more things that have changed!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:24.32,0:15:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's exhausting!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:25.69,0:15:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna think about all of this!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:27.98,0:15:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even wanna know about 'em!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:30.12,0:15:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that's what it was.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:31.28,0:15:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It wasn't that his eyes were bothering him or that he was feeling sick.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:37.47,0:15:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And then those guys{ at the fishery cooperative} had to go and give me that flag, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:41.46,0:15:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The one you waved at the Boatdrift Ceremony?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:43.96,0:15:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that same, stupid flag.{}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:46.59,0:15:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No one was supposed to get lost, \Nas long as I waved it. That's what Manaka said.{again, this has a double meaning, as mentioned earlier. when manaka said it in the beginning, she meant that nobody would doubt the ceremony, and that they would believe in the ceremony. 'mayou' can mean doubt, and that was how she used it. but it can also mean 'to get lost' (as in a maze), and thats how they all look back upon that utterance now.}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:52.29,0:15:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But now...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.43,0:15:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm completely lost.{the maze meaning}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:57.13,0:16:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And so are Manaka, Kaname, Dad, and everyone else.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:01.56,0:16:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them are still lost under the sea.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:03.52,0:16:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just hibernating, \Nso there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:06.96,0:16:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You{r} coming back proves that.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:09.21,0:16:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Still!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:16.95,0:16:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something else happen down there?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:20.23,0:16:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going back down.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:22.53,0:16:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:23.68,0:16:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much you try, getting into Shioshishio is—
Dialogue: 5,0:16:24.88,0:16:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I know that!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:33.87,0:16:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:36.93,0:16:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Miu?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:39.18,0:16:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did I...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:47.59,0:16:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Undies.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:48.79,0:16:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit distracting me!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:50.46,0:16:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:53.43,0:16:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I put it all the way down there.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:57.05,0:16:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so stupid.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:59.59,0:17:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was so happy that Hikari came back.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:03.43,0:17:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was so happy that we were{ now} the same age.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.57,0:17:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was so happy...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:08.86,0:17:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I couldn't even understand something as simple as this.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:12.93,0:17:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari needs his own flag.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:17.43,0:17:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"Flag"?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:23.43,0:17:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So lame.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:25.08,0:17:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
