Dialogue: 5,0:18:46.37,0:18:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:55.69,0:18:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This song.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:57.59,0:18:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... y-yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:59.55,0:19:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The people of Ooshi wanted to make sure it could be heard by everyone sleeping,
Dialogue: 5,0:19:03.81,0:19:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so now it's the five-o'clock song.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:05.90,0:19:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:07.14,0:19:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So everyone was thinking about us...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:10.03,0:19:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All this time.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.12,0:19:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:16.29,0:19:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:18.48,0:19:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:20.07,0:19:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I've changed.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:27.91,0:19:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All this stuff about changing or whatever...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:30.43,0:19:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You were saying the same thing the other day.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:33.64,0:19:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"The other day"?!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:35.81,0:19:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the other day for me!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:37.71,0:19:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,360)}I was scared {...}it would change\N everything between us.{"I was scared that if I told you how I felt, it would change everything between us." - audio matches the second half (ep 12, 18:15)}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:42.09,0:19:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,After I woke up, I finally understood.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:45.84,0:19:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing things change really can be a scary thing.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:49.03,0:19:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:53.83,0:19:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm relieved to see you haven't changed one bit!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:04.63,0:20:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't need to hear that from you! You jerk!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:08.57,0:20:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you're as violent as ever.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:10.90,0:20:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, have you powered up?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:13.06,0:20:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:20.31,0:20:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see it all!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:22.11,0:20:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:23.68,0:20:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna be surprised \Nat all anymore, damn it!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:27.84,0:20:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:29.56,0:20:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:32.21,0:20:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:34.68,0:20:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:41.59,0:20:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I did it in a hurry, so it's not all that great...{lol, i like the momentary switch to ones}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:45.06,0:20:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but I fixed it!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:46.89,0:20:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:48.75,0:20:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hearts. I thought they'd look cute on it.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:51.90,0:20:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And these?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:52.90,0:20:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Butts!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:53.68,0:20:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they're butterflies. {\i1}Butterflies!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:57.09,0:21:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting hearts and butterflies \Non a Boatdrift Ceremony flag...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:00.63,0:21:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys stupid?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:08.55,0:21:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was so happy to see Hikari's smile.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:10.99,0:21:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Butts! Butts!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:12.20,0:21:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No, they're {\i1}butterflies{\i0}.
