Dialogue: 5,0:21:14.06,0:21:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hearts.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:14.34,0:21:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and many things I can't control...{outside of her power, her sphere of influence... i guess... this can be interpreted in several ways}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:14.98,0:21:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Good job.
